quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Iqtarabati assaAAatu wanshaqqaalqamar"
  54,2,"Wa-in yaraw ayatan yuAAridoowayaqooloo sihrun mustamirr"
  54,3,"Wakaththaboo wattabaAAoo ahwaahumwakullu amrin mustaqirr"
  54,4,"Walaqad jaahum mina al-anba-i mafeehi muzdajar"
  54,5,"Hikmatun balighatun famatughnee annuthur"
  54,6,"Fatawalla AAanhum yawma yadAAu addaAAiila shay-in nukur"